snippet.title: The Parrot That Summons Demons - Teaser
snippet.description:
Once the pet of an evil worshiper... Now adopted by an unlucky family! 
Wishlist! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1487200/The_Parrot_That_Summons_Demons/

THE PARROT THAT SUMMONS DEMONS is a horror FMV visual novel featuring a dark and unsettling story with several playable characters and numerous endings.
